Walcott: &quot;We know they tend to be our bogey. We came out of the blocks running and it's nice that we created a lot of chances.&quot;<br />
<br />
Walcott on missing Wenger: &quot;We know our jobs. There's so much experience in this team.&quot;

Wenger on the young midfield: &quot;They were the surprise of the day. I believe that they did very well.&quot;<br />
<br />
Wenger when asked to comment on the FA's ban: &quot;I do not want to judge the judges!&quot;
